OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with spells of
OL,7,Fshowery rain. Rain will be locally
OL,8,Fheavy at times at first, but becoming
OL,9,Fsomewhat drier for a period after
OL,10,Fmidnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FPartly cloudy with showers
OL,13,Fdeveloping, some heavy and merging
OL,14,Finto longer spells of rain, with a
OL,15,Frisk of thunder.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,18,Fchangeable through this period with a
OL,19,Fmix of bright spells and showers.
OL,20,FOften rather breezy.
